definition: to fold/to fold over in layers/to furl/to layer/to pile up/to repeat/to duplicate
old variant of 若[ruo4]/obedient/ancient mythical tree
to overlap/to superimpose/to telescope/to run together/to duplicate/one over another/superposition/an overlap/redundancy/reduplication (in Chinese grammar, e.g. 散散步[san4 san4 bu4] to have a stroll)
to pile up/to put layer upon layer/(Tw) (computing) stack

sentences.english: Silver azide does not dissolve in water or in nitric acid.
sentences.chinese: 叠氨化银不溶于水或硝酸。

sentences.english: The joints of the wood were overlapped and cramped.
sentences.chinese: 这些木头的接头处被叠在一起，用铁箍固定。

sentences.english: The act of turning or winding or folding around a central axis .
sentences.chinese: 围绕一个中心轴翻或绕或叠的动作。

sentences.english: She stood up and began to disrobe, folding each garment neatly.
sentences.chinese: 她站起来开始脱衣服，并把每件衣服叠整齐。

sentences.english: A new method for prestack coherent noise elimination is put forward here.
sentences.chinese: 本文提出了一种新的叠前相干干扰滤除方法。

sentences.english: The cars telescoped after the train crashed.
sentences.chinese: 火车相撞后，车厢叠挤到一块儿了。

sentences.english: The first two carriages of the train telescoped in the crash.
sentences.chinese: 火车撞车时前两节车箱叠嵌在一起了。

sentences.english: The house construction and the view of people overlap.
sentences.chinese: 家屋的建构与人观是叠合在一起的。

sentences.english: The leading research foreland mainly focuses on pre-stack depth domain and elastic wave.
sentences.chinese: 目前的研究前沿主要集中在叠前深度域和弹性波。

sentences.english: Cascading effect through the doorway is the pool.
sentences.chinese: 穿过门洞是叠水效果的水池。

sentences.english: So how high would we have to pile the sandbags?
sentences.chinese: 那么我们需要垒叠多高的沙包防洪呢？

sentences.english: This sediment will then probably be formed into a folded and imbricated structure.
sentences.chinese: 然后这些沉积物可能形成褶皱和叠瓦构造。

sentences.english: Some of his notebooks have pages with four layers underneath.
sentences.chinese: 他的有些笔记本，里页叠着四层。

sentences.english: The capsules are stacked in pairs, with chrome ladders at their entrances.
sentences.chinese: 微型舱是两个叠在一起的，在进口处装有镀铬的扶梯。

sentences.english: It is stressed that the relationship between prestack processing S/N and resolution is important.
sentences.chinese: 强调了叠前处理信噪比与分辨率关系的重要性。

sentences.english: All the people who were standing fell over , piling up on.
sentences.chinese: 站立的人前仆后继，叠在他人身上。
